<html>
<head lang="zh">
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, user-scalable=no">
<title>木鱼</title>
<style>
* {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  line-height; 1em;
}
body {
  background-color: #f4f5f7;
  padding: 15px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  place-content: center;
  place-items: center;
}
.count {
  font-size: 66px;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-family: cursive;
  margin-top: 60px;
  margin-bottom: 30px;
  display: flex;
  place-content: center;
  place-items: center;
}
.center {
  width: 225px;
  margin-top: 30px;
  margin-bottom: 60px;
}
.muyu {
  transform: scale(1);
  transition: .075s;
  width: 225px;
}
.muyu:active { transform: scale(.95); }
@keyframes fade {
  0% {
    opacity: 1;
    margin-top: -120px;
  }
  100% {
    opacity: 0;
    margin-top: -170px;
  }
}
p {
  position: absolute;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fade linear .6s;
}
button {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #4360b7;
  background-color: #e7eeff;
  padding: .65em .9em;
  border-radius: 2em;
  border: none;
  margin: 30px;
  transition: .3s;
}
button:active { background-color: #d6ddee; }
span {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: #ccc;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="count">0</div>本次累积功德
<div class="center">
  <img class="muyu" onkeyup="if (event.keyCode==32) Knock();" onclick="Knock();" src="{{source.sourceIcon}}">
</div>
<button onclick="Bgm();">开启沉浸式BGM(额外消耗流量)</button>
<audio id="bgm" src="http://f3.htcyy.com/play9/973/mp3/2" preload="none" loop hidden></audio>
<span>敲电子木鱼，见机甲佛祖，修赛博真经。</span>
</body>
<script>
function $(t) {
  return document.querySelector(t);
}
function Knock() {
  c = $('.count');
  c.textContent = ++c.textContent;
  x = document.createElement('audio');
  x.src = "data:audio/aac;base64,";
  x.play();
  t = document.createElement('p');
  t.textContent = "功德 + 1，佛祖保佑你";
  $('.center').appendChild(t);
  setTimeout (function () {
    $('p').remove();
    $('audio:not([id])').remove();
  },600);
}
function Bgm() {
  x = $('#bgm');
  s = $('button');
  if (x.paused) {
    x.play();
    s.textContent = "暂停沉浸式BGM";
  } else {
    x.pause();
    s.textContent = "继续沉浸式BGM";
  }
}
</script>
</html>
